<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Overview">Overview</span></h2>
<p>The only TL which needs cargobay upgrades to reach maximum capacity, the Ryu is otherwise a solid choice for a station transporter or light carrier, with good speed, low-to-average cargo space, decent shields and a bigish hangar.
</p>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Background">Background</span></h2>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Physical_Characteristics">Physical Characteristics</span></h2>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Combat"> Combat </span></h2>
<p>The Ryu has a respectable choice of weaponry, but is not a combat vessel and this armament should be used defensively unless the pilot knows what he is doing.
</p>
